      <div class="SOTTO_PARA"><a name="DUCdc399c902ba010058942ff90eb104e4d"></a>Removing the handlebar
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e5922"> </a>First remove throttle control, front brake control and clutch hydraulic control.
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e5924"> </a>Remove the RH switch (1): disconnect connector from main wiring and loosen screws (2).
         </div>
      </div>
